data.description: YOU MUST SEE THIS BEAUTIFUL 1570SF 2 BED/2 BATH HOME WITH DEN THAT CAN BE A THIRD BEDROOM. CURB APPEAL IS OUTSTANDING. THIS IS THE MOST POPULAR FLOORPLAN IN SOLERA. SPLIT LAYOUT WITH PRIMARY BEDROOM ON ONE SIDE AND BEDROOM 2 ALONG WITH DEN ON OTHER SIDE. ALL BLACK APPLIANCES THAT ARE IN FANTASTIC SHAPE. BEIGE CARPET IN BEDROOMS AND DEN WITH TILE THROUGHOUT THE REST OF THE HOUSE. LOCATED IN A QUIET AND YET VIBRANT 55+ COMMUNITY. OUTSTANDING NEIGHBORHOOD WITH AN INCREDIBLE SOCIAL CALENDER TO INCLUDE BUT NOT LIMITED TO TENNIS, PICKLEBALL, BOCCE BALL, FITNESS AND EXERCISE ROOM, OLYMPIC SIZE SWIMMING POOL AND SPA, ACTIVITIES ROOM, POOL TABLE AND PING-PONG. NEW AC SYSTEM. CORIAN COUNTERTOPS. PARTIALLY FENCED IN YARD WITH IRRIGATED DESERT LANDSCAPING. TILE RECENTLY CLEANED AND GROUT SEALED. CEILING FANS IN EVERY ROOM. SECURITY FRONT DOOR. COVERED BACK PATIO. HOUSE IS CLEAN AND WELL MAINTAINED. ALL APPLIANCES STAY. BRING ALL BUYERS TO SEE. IT IS SO CLEAN READY TO MOVE IN.
